name: Angenor
description: A work created inspired by Angenor de Oliveira, better known as Cartola, he was a Brazilian singer, composer, poet and guitarist. One of the greatest successes is the song 'Preciso me Encontrar' (I must find myself) which was precisely where I wanted to create this digital work, this song brings a deep reflection on the creation of our identities and who we are.
